2️⃣ Azure Files (File Storage)
What is Azure Files?
Microsoft Azure Files is a fully managed SMB/NFS-based file share service.

Key Characteristics
Regional service

Shared file system

Accessible from Azure VMs and on-premises

Supports SMB and NFS

Integrated with Active Directory

Scalable and managed

